    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. The high-revving valvetrain remains tight, and the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, positive engagement through all gears. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul and professional reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity. The chassis is further enhanced with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, maintaining factory-spec suspension geometry. Power is delivered effectively via the M-Variable differential lock. While the aesthetic shows minor signs of spirited road use, the powertrain and drivetrain performance remain at a high enthusiast standard.",
