    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2018 Audi A6 that perfectly balances executive luxury with dependable performance. Finished in a sophisticated Moonlight Blue Metallic, the paint retains a deep luster, though in the interest of full disclosure, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small, light scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper. The interior is a smoke-free environment featuring Nougat Brown leather seats that are in excellent shape, save for some very light creasing on the driver's side bolster consistent with careful use. This car has been mechanically pampered; I have maintained a comprehensive file of all service records, including a recent oil service and a fresh set of filters. The turbocharged engine runs smoothly, and the Quattro all-wheel-drive system provides a planted, confident feel on the road. All electronics, including the pop-up MMI display, heated steering wheel, and sunroof, are fully operational. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, meaning no immediate maintenance is required. This is a well-maintained, honest vehicle ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
